WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:08.886
Hey, good morning family. How are you all doing today? I’m going to talk to you about the angelic visitations I’ve had.

00:00:08.887 --> 00:00:20.330
I’ve had several angelic visitations over the years and the Lord has been amazing; I’ve seen some really cool stuff.

00:00:20.331 --> 00:00:30.742
This time, we were just praying. It was a normal night in the same house and everything was the same.

00:00:30.743 --> 00:00:45.136
We were praying and went to bed, and all of a sudden my wife and I were woken up out of our sleep. It was early in the morning and the whole house shook.

00:00:45.137 --> 00:00:57.911
It sounded like the whole roof was going to come off our house and my wife said, 'Oh, did you hear that?'She woke me and I said, 'Yes, I heard it. It woke me up, too.

00:00:57.912 --> 00:01:12.239
I think somebody’s trying to break into our house,'and I said, 'Let me go check.'I grabbed my pistol and went to check our home to make sure that nobody was there.

00:01:12.240 --> 00:01:29.503
All of a sudden, I looked out while standing by the door. I stood up and my eyes were opened to the spirit realm. I saw four demons.

00:01:29.504 --> 00:01:44.712
They were four demonic spirits covered with scales, with nasty-looking hair growing out of them and warts.

00:01:44.713 --> 00:01:54.191
Their eyes were slanted and red. One had a pig-looking nose with tusks coming up.

00:01:54.192 --> 00:02:08.096
The other was completely black; there was no shape to it. It looked kind of like a ghost, but it was just a black, misty-looking thing.

00:02:08.097 --> 00:02:20.110
The others were different shapes. I’m not going to give any more glory to it, but every single one of them was there, trying to get into the house.

00:02:20.111 --> 00:02:29.503
They shook the roof of the house in the natural, and like I said, it startled both of us and woke us up, but they couldn't get in.

00:02:29.504 --> 00:02:40.729
The Lord didn't show me this at the time, but I saw them grunting and hissing, carrying on while passing by on the street.

00:02:40.730 --> 00:02:52.917
I didn't understand why they couldn't come past. All of a sudden, I saw massive, humongous angels chained together.

00:02:52.918 --> 00:03:27.220
Their arms were linked together, like when you cross your arms with someone else; that’s how they were standing.

00:03:27.221 --> 00:03:37.636
They were standing strong, and the demonic spirits were hitting against those angelic beings, but they couldn't get past them.

00:03:37.637 --> 00:03:43.969
Every night before we go to bed, we put chain-linked angels all around our house and commission them.

00:03:43.970 --> 00:03:54.164
We thank you, Lord, that the angels are surrounding our house, that no devil in hell can come across the bloodline or the angels.

00:03:54.165 --> 00:04:07.317
The angels are protecting us as we sleep, just like we prayed.

00:04:07.318 --> 00:04:16.098
It took me aback so much that I yelled when I saw this, 'Praise God! Wow!

00:04:16.099 --> 00:04:40.159
Praise the Lord!'I saw the angels protecting us, and whenever they heard me praising the Lord, they all looked over, turned their bodies, and started looking at me, saying, 'Praise the Lord!'They started worshiping the Lord with me.

00:04:40.160 --> 00:04:45.655
I turned around and said, 'Whoa!'because it took me aback because it was so loud.

00:04:45.656 --> 00:04:53.752
Their voices were so loud it sounded like sirens, like trumpets, like a blast.

00:04:53.753 --> 00:05:02.899
'Praise the Lord!'They didn't say it individually; they said it together.

00:05:02.900 --> 00:05:08.911
They said, 'Praise the Lord,'and when they did, it echoed throughout the area.

00:05:08.912 --> 00:05:18.550
You could hear it in the spirit realm; it was so loud you would have to hold your ears. They started praising the Lord with me.

00:05:18.551 --> 00:05:35.697
Every time they worshiped, they turned to see what I was doing and as I praised the Lord, they started praising the Lord too. It became a chain and we just started praising the Lord.

00:05:35.698 --> 00:05:56.577
At that time, I saw the glory coming from the heavens through a portal, and I could see shafts of light coming through that portal, making those angels glow.

00:05:56.577 --> 00:06:03.813
They started glowing with a heavenly glory even brighter as they praised the Lord.

00:06:03.814 --> 00:06:24.159
Those shafts of light were coming out of the heavens and making them stronger—it was like it was giving them 'super juice.'They were praising the Lord with me and getting shinier.

00:06:24.160 --> 00:06:33.678
I had completely forgotten about the demonic spirits because I was caught up in the glory of worshiping the angels at the same time.

00:06:33.679 --> 00:06:46.210
Every time I said, 'Thank you, Jesus,'they would say, 'Thank you, Jesus.'This went on for quite some time.

00:06:46.211 --> 00:06:56.117
I was taken aback by what I was seeing in the spirit realm; it really was amazing. After all this happened, I saw the glory come down.

00:06:56.118 --> 00:07:03.393
It was around 4 or 5 in the morning now, and I had to go to work the next day by eight.

00:07:03.394 --> 00:07:10.711
I went and laid down a little bit and dozed off, but it was hard to get more rest.

00:07:10.712 --> 00:07:22.101
I got to work the next day at the church for an all-staff meeting and the pastor, Pastor Mark, saw me sitting in the front.

00:07:22.102 --> 00:07:31.192
I told him, 'I want to tell you what happened last night.'He said, 'Brandon, I don't doubt it at all. As you were talking, you were shining.

00:07:31.193 --> 00:07:49.176
I can see the glory shining on you.'There was actually a presence of the Lord on me from the visitation the night before, making me shine a little bit.

00:07:49.177 --> 00:08:01.803
Pastor Mark could see the glory on me. It’s just amazing. That’s how you know I live by faith.

00:08:01.804 --> 00:08:07.839
I expect angelic visitations and manifestations of the glory in my house.

00:08:07.840 --> 00:08:14.932
I expect God to do the impossible and I receive it. Let me tell you another one.

00:08:14.933 --> 00:08:20.987
There have been times when I’ve gone through a shady part of town and felt nervous.

00:08:20.988 --> 00:08:37.179
One time, I went to the gas station late at night—or it seemed late because it was winter and the sun goes down so early.

00:08:37.180 --> 00:08:56.079
I was nervous to get out of the car because of where I was and thought, 'Okay, here we go.'I went out there, and all of a sudden—because God loves you all and is compassionate—He opened my eyes for my comfort.

00:08:56.080 --> 00:09:13.093
He said, 'Look over, son.'I looked to my left, and there was a massive angel standing there watching over me as I was pumping gas.

00:09:13.094 --> 00:09:27.504
The angel was at attention. He had muscles upon muscles. He made Arnold Schwarzenegger look like a little weenie, like a little wimpy baby guy, or even some big bodybuilder, Mr. Universe.

00:09:27.505 --> 00:09:48.033
Olympics, like some guy that's ripped and has been eating nothing but protein, but this angel had muscle upon muscle and he was standing there decked out with this garb on, it looked like some kind of armor, and he was looking out at attention, watching over me.

00:09:48.034 --> 00:10:05.220
And when I saw that, it took me back. It took my breath and I went, "Whoa."Because it's one of those things that shows God cares. God cares. And it blessed me so as he was watching out for me.

00:10:05.221 --> 00:10:14.966
It just shows that we have angels that keep charge over us and they bear us up in their hands lest we dash our foot against a stone.

00:10:14.967 --> 00:10:21.098
He promised us in Psalm 91 that he would do this. He promised us that he would take care of us.

00:10:21.099 --> 00:10:27.726
Do you believe it? Do you believe it? That Jesus is still the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:10:27.727 --> 00:10:36.639
And what he would do for the people in the Bible, he'll do for you. He'll protect you. Let me tell you another one.

00:10:36.640 --> 00:10:47.283
I was working at the church and I told you all about the healings whenever I'd led prayer and the angels bringing in hearts for people that needed hearts.

00:10:47.284 --> 00:10:58.785
For whatever reason, it was another heart testimony and I was just vacuuming the floor and I'm seeing over in this realm of the spirits when this happens.

00:10:58.786 --> 00:11:24.860
But this time the angel touched me and I literally thought I was going to come up out of my skin whenever he did it because I felt it on my shoulder and I was the only one in the room vacuuming the church and I went, "Whoa."You get a little startled because the angel touched me like that and I turned around and I'm just seeing in the realm of spirit.

00:11:24.861 --> 00:11:41.077
It's not a physical manifestation, nothing like that; I'm looking in the realm of the spirit, but he touched me in the natural and he said, "I've come to give Jim a heart."He goes, "You need to go and tell Jim that I've brought him a heart."He's believing.

00:11:41.078 --> 00:11:45.839
He's been praying for a heart. They're believing for a miracle because Jim had a bad heart.

00:11:45.840 --> 00:11:51.968
And he was one of the other janitors on staff. And his blood pressure would drop bad, really bad.

00:11:51.969 --> 00:11:59.919
