00:11:59.920 --> 00:12:05.040
So the angel brought this heart and I could see in the spirit realm like I'm seeing my son right now.

00:12:05.041 --> 00:12:15.518
I mean it was that clear and the angel had a heart in his hand just like this—and, you know what, I take that back—it was in both hands. He had it in there.

00:12:15.519 --> 00:12:39.698
He brought it to me and he said, "Go and tell Jim that I brought the heart for him."So I said, "Wow, okay, what an honor."So I walk down the hall and I get all the way down the hall and Jim was in room number two because the rooms weren't labeled at this church, and he was in room two or three and I was cleaning on the back side of room 24.

